commit.message: Added images and fixed styling before presentation
(UI) Implemented drop down menu for "Get Help"

Username and room list

Added username input field
Prepared code for displaying room lists and selecting room.
UI - Buttons now direct to different pages

Implemented additionnal route

Implemented additional route to return a list of rooms associated to the volunteer

Barebones server

REST API server is setup.
Can:
- Create users
- Assign a user to a volunteer
- Send messages back and forth
- Geting of messages returns only unrequested messages

Scrapped project.

Project will be restarted using WebClient-Server architecture.

Minor layout changes

Buttons on home are centered vertically
Removed FAB from Volunteer tabbed view.
